detailedDescription.articleBody: The Goldman Sachs Group, Inc., is an American multinational investment bank and financial services company headquartered in New York City.

detailedDescription.articleBody: OP Financial Group is one of the largest financial companies in Finland. It consists of 180 cooperative banks and their central organization. “OP” stands for “osuuspankki” in Finnish, literally “cooperative bank”. The financial group has over 1.4 million customer-owners. The group offers retail and commercial banking services all over Finland as well as insurance services.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Visa Inc. is an American multinational financial services corporation headquartered in Foster City, California, United States. It facilitates electronic funds transfers throughout the world, most commonly through Visa-branded credit cards, debit cards and prepaid cards.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: वीजा इंक, एक अमेरिकी बहुराष्ट्रीय वित्तीय सेवा निगम है, जिसका मुख्यालय फोस्टर सिटी, कैलिफ़ोर्निया, संयुक्त राज्य अमेरिका में है, यह दुनिया भर में इलेक्ट्रॉनिक फंड ट्रांसफर की सुविधा देता है, जो आमतौर पर वीज़ा-ब्रांडेड क्रेडिट कार्ड, डेबिट कार्ड और प्रीपेड कार्ड के माध्यम से होता है।

detailedDescription.articleBody: Daycoval is a midsize Brazil-based bank that provides personal and corporate banking services, such as credit, investment banking, credit card, brokerage, trade bill collection, custodian and deposit services, as well as payroll loans and auto loans under the Daycred brand name.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: Daycoval ब्राजील स्थित एक मध्यम आकार का बैंक है जो व्यक्तिगत और कॉर्पोरेट बैंकिंग सेवाएं प्रदान करता है, जैसे कि क्रेडिट, निवेश बैंकिंग, क्रेडिट कार्ड, ब्रोकरेज, व्यापार बिल संग्रह, संरक्षक और जमा सेवाएं, साथ ही Daycred ब्रांड नाम के तहत पेरोल ऋण और ऑटो ऋण।

detailedDescription.articleBody: The Carlyle Group is an American multinational private equity, alternative asset management and financial services corporation. It specializes in corporate private equity, real assets, and private credit.
